column1: Table 1: Brain structures volume AAL116 atlas across the three brain health groups (OBH, GBH, DBH).

Note: The table reports mean gray matter volumes (in mm³) for all brain structures defined in the AAL116 atlas across the three brain health groups (OBH, GBH, DBH). For each region, a one-way ANOVA tested group differences in volume, followed by Bonferroni-corrected post hoc comparisons. Columns include the group means, the F statistic, the uncorrected p value (p_uncorr), the Bonferroni-adjusted p value (p_bonferroni), and an indicator of statistical significance after correction. Significant results reflect volumetric differences across brain health levels.
